{"context":"취미로 운동에 대해 이야기하며","dialogue":[{"speaker":"A","text":"운동 좋아해요?","romanization":"undong jotahaeyo?","translation":"Do you like sports?"},{"speaker":"B","text":"네, 수영을/를 좋아해요.","romanization":"ne, suyeongeul/reul jotahaeyo.","translation":"Yes, I like swimming."},{"speaker":"A","text":"자주 해요?","romanization":"jaju haeyo?","translation":"Do you play often?"},{"speaker":"B","text":"주말마다 해요.","romanization":"jumalmada haeyo.","translation":"I play every weekend."}]}